Use Case 1
Game is started
Player clicks play 
Gameplay starts
Player goes through the level killing enemies
Player dies
Gameplay starts over
Player goes through the level killing enemies
Player presses escape and exits game
Player comes back and opens the game 
Game starts
Player presses options
Player changes audio settings
Player presses back
Player presses play
Game starts from previous save state
Player progresses through the story
Player kills final boss
Player presses escape and clicks exit
Game ends

